Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.40,0:22:16.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集的又是些一般的提議呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.63,0:22:23.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與愛{\fnzhunyuan}洸{\r}的格式與紀律相違的提議
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.10,0:22:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都被學園祭實行委員會給剔除了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.63,0:22:37.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此  還是很無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.23,0:22:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.39,0:22:54.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像混起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.21,0:23:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是昨天聖櫻學生會幹事送來的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.92,0:23:05.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  整理的時候似乎不小心混進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.23,0:23:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲避球大會？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.10,0:23:12.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意圖也算清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.69,0:23:14.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.84,0:23:18.39,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「學園對抗賽 躲避球大會  6月15日 決賽」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.45,0:23:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不參加嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.60,0:23:26.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  參加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.91,0:03:20.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.38,0:00:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:08.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好感動哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.72,0:00:11.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:15.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  這些就放在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.92,0:00:18.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  OK
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.95,0:00:20.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.76,0:00:24.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.73,0:00:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說可以嘗試著做一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,0:00:29.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不知道你們打算怎麼播放呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:31.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得的機會  封套也一起做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.55,0:00:33.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要也登上聖櫻的網頁？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.74,0:00:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.76,0:00:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都登上去吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.98,0:00:39.94,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登上去吧  登上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.05,0:00:41.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.34,0:01:06.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是糖果研究會的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.23,0:01:07.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想拜託一件事  可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.45,0:01:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  當然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.85,0:01:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自學生會室翻新以來  已經過了兩周了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.77,0:01:13.71,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}星期一就太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.90,0:01:15.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.67,0:01:16.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只說一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉球時手不要伸開  應該用身體曲成團抱住球來捕捉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.55,0:01:20.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.35,0:01:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲避的時候  應該向對方的慣用手那一側躲避
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.88,0:01:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.08,0:01:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為若向慣用手的外側發力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.03,0:01:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反應速度會更慢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.68,0:01:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量也相對較小
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.69,0:01:30.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.30,0:01:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.83,0:01:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芽  真是博識啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.65,0:01:40.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在問別人之前  好歹自己先在網上搜索一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.56,0:01:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好我會碰巧  偶然  不時地從這門前路過…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:21.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是偶然路過而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.59,0:03:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.08,0:03:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.67,0:03:32.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:33.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去壘球部幫忙了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.95,0:03:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒甚麼精神呢  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.39,0:03:40.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:41.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀…其實呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.18,0:03:43.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒——！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.79,0:03:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在說這樣的話  沒有時間去找代替的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.57,0:03:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是沒有辦法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.85,0:03:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壘球部的神崎明天無論如何都要去打工
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.52,0:04:02.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之  要另外找個人代替才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先說好了  我可不是那種甚麼事都幫一把的老好人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.08,0:04:06.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.15,0:04:07.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉的時候  身體要曲成團
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.21,0:04:09.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲避的時候  應該向對方的慣用手那一側躲避
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.11,0:04:11.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毅力不夠！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到球的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.38,0:04:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.28,0:04:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是學園躲避球對抗賽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.35,0:04:23.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（拼盡全力  加油吧!!）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.72,0:04:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我們聖櫻策劃  號召附近的高中參加的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.13,0:04:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園躲避球對抗大賽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:32.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好在能有五所高校響應
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.05,0:04:36.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於今天在這裡聚集
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.91,0:04:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:55.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個  這個…看準對方的慣用手…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.09,0:04:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.11,0:05:00.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲避的時候  要看準對方的慣用手那一側
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:04.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉的時候  身體曲成團抱住！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:07.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇氣還不夠！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.79,0:05:08.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到球的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.72,0:05:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.65,0:05:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:29.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是愛{\fnzhunyuan}洸{\r}學生會會長  角澤多佳子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.53,0:05:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:35.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.26,0:05:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好不容易來我們這兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.91,0:05:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:45.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是佈置的了不起的學生會室呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.85,0:05:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  謝謝稱讚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.05,0:05:53.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的籌備  感覺做得也很出色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.20,0:05:58.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「隊伍請務必要展現學生會幹事的風采」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:05:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「比賽結束之後  我們還準備了聯誼會」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今誰也沒有想過  各個學校之間能建立起一種橫向的聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.14,0:06:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許這樣可以找到  各自擔負著的問題的解決的突破口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個開端就是對抗賽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…也許我只是單純地想  大家友好相處會更快樂些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.84,0:06:38.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.60,0:06:45.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做炒麵的材料不夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:48.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一會再見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.12,0:06:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  天宮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:06:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喊學美就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:01.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學美同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.04,0:07:06.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見  多佳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:11.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多佳？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.90,0:07:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以發郵件聯繫嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.15,0:07:22.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.89,0:07:26.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我也要  郵箱地址給我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咳咳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天能在百忙之中聚集各位  真是十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是值得紀念的第一屆學生會幹事聯誼會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.20,0:07:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總而言之  複雜的話就不多說了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為大家不先做好朋友的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:48.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不會有甚麼真正的好意見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天大家就吃些好吃的東西  高興地聊聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:53.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣了  如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.69,0:07:58.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:00.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.53,0:08:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要那樣的話  躲避球不就已經足夠了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.13,0:08:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得聚在了一起  說些有意義的話題會比較好…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.07,0:08:20.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  又不是來玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.12,0:08:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.95,0:08:24.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺一定要商談一下的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.02,0:08:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不成體統呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.58,0:08:33.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底想做甚麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.13,0:08:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做點甚麼有意義的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.37,0:08:41.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.86,0:08:46.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.68,0:08:48.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意義的話題甚麼的…完全沒有準備啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:08:56.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的  蜜柑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.55,0:09:00.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本日的議題是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓學園生活變得生機勃勃  令人興奮的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.85,0:09:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼做才好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.71,0:09:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生機勃勃？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:13.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人興奮？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.16,0:09:14.12,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是做甚麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.34,0:09:15.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不成體統呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.76,0:09:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.02,0:09:17.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學美…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.42,0:09:17.76,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是甚麼意思  不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:19.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園祭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:21.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討論一下這個怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.94,0:09:24.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論哪個學校  都差不多是要準備這個的時期了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.07,0:09:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為共同的議題不是正適合嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛{\fnzhunyuan}洸{\r}學園的同學既然這麼說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.47,0:09:33.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作決定的可是聖櫻學園的同學哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:39.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  就…就這麼辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:41.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:42.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果  結果學美就這麼一言未發地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:44.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在角澤多佳子同學的帶領下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.86,0:09:46.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算是不至於冷場
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.66,0:09:48.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學生會幹事聯誼會  就這樣消化不良地結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.34,0:09:49.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必介意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也會演變成那樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.97,0:09:56.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:03.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲避球比賽也算是盛況空前了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:06.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先對現有的成績感到滿足吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔  加些調料
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:16.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:20.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.98,0:10:24.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊  大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇——
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.58,0:10:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要一碗炸醬麵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.68,0:10:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.81,0:10:45.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.62,0:10:56.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我為你擔心了好半天呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.04,0:10:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.04,0:11:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.67,0:11:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:07.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:09.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園祭…嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:10.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.37,0:11:11.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向前…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.38,0:11:12.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好像都很困呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.26,0:11:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我們叫醒的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.75,0:11:16.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（前方是愛{\fnzhunyuan}洸{\r}學園站）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.30,0:11:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看一下這個的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本就能瞭解愛{\fnzhunyuan}洸{\r}的學園祭是怎麼一回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.73,0:11:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有甚麼不知道的就問我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.17,0:11:32.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大部分的問題我都是能答上來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.74,0:11:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然打擾你真是對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.22,0:11:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒甚麼  倒是我這邊該為昨天的事說聲對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:58.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們有你們自己的做法…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.50,0:12:29.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在擔心  是不是被你們討厭了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.93,0:12:31.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這回事  多虧了多佳我們才不至於變得很尷尬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.93,0:12:43.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是幫了我們大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  蜜柑？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.79,0:12:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？啊  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:14.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是愛……吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:21.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是愛……呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.65,0:13:24.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:39.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你們覺得怎麼樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.01,0:13:41.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於學園祭  你們找到甚麼靈感了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:55.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有點失去信心了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:14:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多佳這裡的學園祭真的很出色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.54,0:14:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.27,0:14:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像突然出現了一個難以達成的目標一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.45,0:14:11.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼努力都趕不上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.65,0:14:12.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  不管是學校的水準  還是學生的數量都不是一個檔次的  沒辦法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:17.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  既然資料也拿到了  我們就回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.91,0:14:20.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  給這裡添麻煩就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.18,0:14:22.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝了  角澤學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.64,0:14:24.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我認為角澤學姐是一位非常出色的學生會長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我們也會努力辦一個不輸給…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:31.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我們是不可能贏的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.24,0:14:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們也會努力辦一個不輸給愛{\fnzhunyuan}洸{\r}的學園祭的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候請一定要來玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了  多佳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:43.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.91,0:14:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒甚麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.94,0:14:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們走好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天謝謝你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:15:00.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一個人來的話總覺得有點心虛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:03.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  反正我也挺開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:05.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是甚麼值得感謝的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:07.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們說  角澤學姐最後究竟是想說甚麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:13.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚麼啊…  光香你一直在想這個啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是想讓我們付咖啡的錢啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.45,0:15:17.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.17,0:15:22.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學美是怎麼想的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.07,0:15:25.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒甚麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:29.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們走好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.65,0:15:33.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:43.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.82,0:15:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的晚飯是豬肉泡菜和四季豆豆莢的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.98,0:15:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:16:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是不是進入叛逆期了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:02.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向前…衝！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:04.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（學園祭構思筆記）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:11.15,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（生機勃勃  令人興奮）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:14.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.35,0:16:18.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學…學美  有甚麼話想對哥哥說的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後再說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.74,0:16:23.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？現在？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.77,0:16:31.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能等明天再說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.16,0:16:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能在電話裡說嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.92,0:16:43.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好困啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:44.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.16,0:16:47.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就想說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.97,0:16:48.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在電話裡說不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.58,0:17:34.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學校…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學校集合——
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.02,0:17:51.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  你到底想幹甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:20.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種時間把我們叫出來…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:27.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.94,0:18:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道多佳她想說甚麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:35.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她想說甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.48,0:18:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多佳是想告訴我們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.63,0:18:43.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實不管甚麼樣的學園祭  我們都能辦起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.96,0:18:47.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像多佳的學校那樣出色的學園祭也辦起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.61,0:18:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的學園祭也是能辦起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:52.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的學園祭？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.08,0:18:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個我還不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.38,0:19:01.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是把愛{\fnzhunyuan}洸{\r}的學園祭照抄過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用以愛{\fnzhunyuan}洸{\r}那樣的學園祭為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:08.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是由我們所構思的  只有我們能辦得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.69,0:19:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界獨一無二
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.97,0:19:13.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦得到的  因為甚麼事情還都沒有決定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.07,0:19:15.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是一片空白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.01,0:19:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一片空白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.14,0:19:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  甚麼都辦得到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.37,0:19:27.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我們來描繪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:30.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一片空白之上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.82,0:19:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界獨一無二
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.25,0:19:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只屬於我們的學園祭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.08,0:19:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是一個人  而是大家一起——
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.58,0:19:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.85,0:19:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只屬於我們的…嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.60,0:19:45.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是才被人教訓過說要再認真一點嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.75,0:19:50.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  聽了剛剛的那番話  總覺得我們辦得到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.98,0:19:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四話  『廣告推行之卷』
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.15,0:19:57.12,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}一定才剛剛開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.65,0:19:59.35,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}千里之行始於足下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.93,0:20:01.85,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}一開始的時候無論是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:06.93,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}都不可以恐慌  這才是最重要的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:13.83,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}選擇了自己所喜歡的道路真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:18.22,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,600)}神啊  我要因此而感謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:24.29,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,300)}如今的Lucky  請好好地珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.73,0:20:26.88,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Happy並持續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:38.00,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}來吧  保持著這股勢頭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.72,0:21:07.90,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Bang！Bang！Bang！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.70,0:21:25.02,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}是呢  Lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.14,0:21:30.26,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}如今正是時候  Happy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.12,0:21:34.78,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}把握住機會
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.21,0:23:47.25,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}努力地生活下去吧
